    "severity": "High",
    "confidence": "high",
    "title": "RiskManager asset disallow leaves balance accounting inconsistent",
    "locations": ["managers/RiskManager.sol:184-197", "managers/RiskManager.sol:242-252"],
    "claim": "When assets are disallowed from a subvault via disallowSubvaultAssets, the existing balance in subvaultState is not cleaned up.",
    "impact": "Disallowed assets remain in the subvaultState.balance and cannot be withdrawn, permanently locking those funds as the RiskManager will reject any balance modifications for disallowed assets.",
    "paths": ["1. Assets are allowed and deposited into subvault", "2. Asset is later disallowed", "3. Attempts to modify subvault balance fail with NotAllowedAsset", "4. Funds trapped permanently"]
