    "claim": "When Oracle.removeSupportedAssets is called, the associated queues in ShareModule are not notified and may retain stale state.",
    "impact": "Queues for removed assets will retain stale price data and cannot process new reports, causing deposit/redeem operations to fail or use invalid prices.",
    "paths": ["1. Asset is supported and used in queues", "2. Asset is removed from Oracle", "3. Queue still holds stale price data", "4. Subsequent queue operations fail or use invalid prices"]
  },
